{
  "id": "63ca0177aa9d3e001d53f9a0",
  "title": "線を引くUI",
  "created": 1674183037,
  "updated": 1674444311,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "63ca0177aa9d3e001d53f9a0",
      "text": "線を引くUI",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674183037,
      "updated": 1674194427
    },
    {
      "id": "63cdfe0baff09e00000fcf18",
      "text": "二つの要素の間に線を引き、要素が移動されてもつながり続けて欲しい、というユースケースをどうやって実現するか\t",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674444299,
      "updated": 1674444302
    },
    {
      "id": "63cdfe0baff09e00000fcf19",
      "text": "\tKozanebaの線を引くUIを改善しようと考えている\t",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674444299,
      "updated": 1674444308
    },
    {
      "id": "63cdfe0baff09e00000fcf1a",
      "text": "\t一旦内部の設計の都合は置いといて「線を引くUI」にはどのようなものがあるか考える",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674444299,
      "updated": 1674444299
    },
    {
      "id": "63ca043eaff09e0000612825",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674183743,
      "updated": 1674444311
    },
    {
      "id": "63ca04a7aff09e0000612828",
      "text": "実装方法1:",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674183847,
      "updated": 1674194436
    },
    {
      "id": "63ca2e03aff09e00009d9e28",
      "text": " 線を引くモードを導入する",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674194436,
      "updated": 1674194436
    },
    {
      "id": "63ca2e03aff09e00009d9e29",
      "text": " 要素Aと要素Bをクリックすると線が引かれる",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674194436,
      "updated": 1674194436
    },
    {
      "id": "63ca2e03aff09e00009d9e2a",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674194436,
      "updated": 1674194436
    },
    {
      "id": "63ca2e03aff09e00009d9e2b",
      "text": "実装方法2:",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674194436,
      "updated": 1674194436
    },
    {
      "id": "63ca2e03aff09e00009d9e2c",
      "text": " 線を引くモードを導入する",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674194436,
      "updated": 1674194436
    },
    {
      "id": "63ca2e03aff09e00009d9e2d",
      "text": " 要素Aでポインターダウン、要素Bでポインターアップすると線が引かれる",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674194436,
      "updated": 1674194436
    },
    {
      "id": "63ca2e03aff09e00009d9e2e",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674194436,
      "updated": 1674194436
    },
    {
      "id": "63ca2e03aff09e00009d9e2f",
      "text": "実装方法3:",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674194436,
      "updated": 1674194436
    },
    {
      "id": "63ca2e03aff09e00009d9e30",
      "text": " 複数の要素を選択する",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674194436,
      "updated": 1674194436
    },
    {
      "id": "63ca2e03aff09e00009d9e31",
      "text": "　 コンテキストメニューが現れる",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674194436,
      "updated": 1674194436
    },
    {
      "id": "63ca2e03aff09e00009d9e32",
      "text": " メニューから「線を引く」を選ぶ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674194436,
      "updated": 1674194436
    },
    {
      "id": "63ca2e03aff09e00009d9e33",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674194436,
      "updated": 1674194436
    },
    {
      "id": "63ca2e03aff09e00009d9e34",
      "text": "実装方法4:",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674194436,
      "updated": 1674194436
    },
    {
      "id": "63ca2e03aff09e00009d9e35",
      "text": " グローバルのメニューで「線を追加」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674194436,
      "updated": 1674194436
    },
    {
      "id": "63ca2e03aff09e00009d9e36",
      "text": "　両端がnullの線ができる",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674194436,
      "updated": 1674194436
    },
    {
      "id": "63ca2e03aff09e00009d9e37",
      "text": "　それを要素A、要素Bにドラッグドロップすると接続される",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674194436,
      "updated": 1674194436
    },
    {
      "id": "63ca2e03aff09e00009d9e38",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674194436,
      "updated": 1674194436
    },
    {
      "id": "63ca2e03aff09e00009d9e39",
      "text": "実装方法5:",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674194436,
      "updated": 1674194436
    },
    {
      "id": "63ca2e03aff09e00009d9e3a",
      "text": " 要素Aのクリックでハンドルが現れる",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674194436,
      "updated": 1674194436
    },
    {
      "id": "63ca2e03aff09e00009d9e3b",
      "text": " ハンドルを要素Bにドラッグドロップすると線が引かれる",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674194436,
      "updated": 1674194436
    },
    {
      "id": "63ca2e03aff09e00009d9e3c",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674194436,
      "updated": 1674194436
    },
    {
      "id": "63ca2e03aff09e00009d9e3d",
      "text": "線を引くモードについて",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674194436,
      "updated": 1674194436
    },
    {
      "id": "63ca2e03aff09e00009d9e3e",
      "text": "　まとめて線を引くならモードに入るのが楽",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674194436,
      "updated": 1674194436
    },
    {
      "id": "63ca2e03aff09e00009d9e3f",
      "text": "　線を引いて要素を動かして、が頻繁に切り替わるならその度にモード切り替えが必要になって手間",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674194436,
      "updated": 1674194436
    },
    {
      "id": "63ca2e03aff09e00009d9e40",
      "text": "　　「いま自分がどのモードか」を把握する必要がある",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674194436,
      "updated": 1674194436
    },
    {
      "id": "63ca2e03aff09e00009d9e41",
      "text": "　　要素を動かそうとして線を引いてしまう人が出る",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674194436,
      "updated": 1674194436
    },
    {
      "id": "63ca2e03aff09e00009d9e42",
      "text": "　Google Slideは実装方法2",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674194436,
      "updated": 1674194436
    },
    {
      "id": "63ca2e03aff09e00009d9e43",
      "text": "  ドラッグドロップの対象は要素自身ではなくハンドル",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674194436,
      "updated": 1674194436
    },
    {
      "id": "63ca2e03aff09e00009d9e44",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674194436,
      "updated": 1674194436
    },
    {
      "id": "63ca2e03aff09e00009d9e45",
      "text": "実装方法3",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674194436,
      "updated": 1674194436
    },
    {
      "id": "63ca2e03aff09e00009d9e46",
      "text": " 現状のKozanebaの実装",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674194436,
      "updated": 1674194436
    },
    {
      "id": "63ca2e03aff09e00009d9e47",
      "text": " 二要素間の関係に限らず表現できることがメリット",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674194436,
      "updated": 1674194436
    },
    {
      "id": "63ca2e03aff09e00009d9e48",
      "text": " 近いものに線を引くなら許容できる",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674194436,
      "updated": 1674194436
    },
    {
      "id": "63ca2e03aff09e00009d9e49",
      "text": " 遠くのものに線を引こうとした時や入り組んだ配置の時に「範囲選択」で他のものを巻き込んでしまう",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674194436,
      "updated": 1674194436
    },
    {
      "id": "63ca2e03aff09e00009d9e4a",
      "text": " 　運用による回避手段",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674194436,
      "updated": 1674194436
    },
    {
      "id": "63ca2e03aff09e00009d9e4b",
      "text": " 　　対象要素を近くに移動する",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674194436,
      "updated": 1674194436
    },
    {
      "id": "63ca2e03aff09e00009d9e4c",
      "text": " 　　線を引く",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674194436,
      "updated": 1674194436
    },
    {
      "id": "63ca2e03aff09e00009d9e4d",
      "text": " 　　元の場所に戻す",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674194436,
      "updated": 1674194436
    },
    {
      "id": "63ca2e03aff09e00009d9e4e",
      "text": " 　これは面倒！",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674194436,
      "updated": 1674194436
    },
    {
      "id": "63ca2e03aff09e00009d9e4f",
      "text": " 　線の機能を作って使ってみているうちに、思っていた以上にこういう状況が多発して面倒だと気づいた",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674194436,
      "updated": 1674194436
    },
    {
      "id": "63ca2e03aff09e00009d9e50",
      "text": " 　　多項関係を掛けるメリットを上回るデメリットだと思うようになった",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674194436,
      "updated": 1674194436
    },
    {
      "id": "63ca2e03aff09e00009d9e51",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674194436,
      "updated": 1674194436
    },
    {
      "id": "63ca2e03aff09e00009d9e52",
      "text": "実装方法4",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674194436,
      "updated": 1674194436
    },
    {
      "id": "63ca2e03aff09e00009d9e53",
      "text": " Keynoteは線のボタンを押した時点で線が追加される",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674194436,
      "updated": 1674194436
    },
    {
      "id": "63ca2e03aff09e00009d9e54",
      "text": " 　要素に接続はしない？",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674194436,
      "updated": 1674194436
    },
    {
      "id": "63ca2e03aff09e00009d9e55",
      "text": " Google Slideも「線を引くモード」でクリックをするとこれになる",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674194436,
      "updated": 1674194436
    },
    {
      "id": "63ca2e03aff09e00009d9e56",
      "text": " 一時的に「どこにもつながっていない線」ができるので「線とは要素を繋ぐものである」と定義していると問題が起きる",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674194436,
      "updated": 1674194436
    },
    {
      "id": "63ca2e03aff09e00009d9e57",
      "text": " 　設計時に注意が必要",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674194436,
      "updated": 1674194436
    },
    {
      "id": "63ca2e03aff09e00009d9e58",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674194436,
      "updated": 1674194436
    },
    {
      "id": "63ca2e03aff09e00009d9e59",
      "text": "実装方法5",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674194436,
      "updated": 1674194436
    },
    {
      "id": "63ca2e03aff09e00009d9e5a",
      "text": "　Miroの実装",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674194436,
      "updated": 1674194436
    },
    {
      "id": "63ca2e03aff09e00009d9e5b",
      "text": "　　現状のKozanebaも要素をクリックするとコンテキストメニューが出るので「一時的なモードに入っている」という点では同じ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674194436,
      "updated": 1674194436
    },
    {
      "id": "63ca2e03aff09e00009d9e5c",
      "text": " 　　ハンドルを出すことはできる",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674194436,
      "updated": 1674194436
    },
    {
      "id": "63ca2e03aff09e00009d9e5d",
      "text": "　　　ハンドルでポインターダウンした時点で「一時的なメニューを出すモード」が「一時的な線を引くモード」に切り替わる必要がある",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674194436,
      "updated": 1674194436
    },
    {
      "id": "63ca2e03aff09e00009d9e5e",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674194436,
      "updated": 1674194436
    },
    {
      "id": "63ca0611aff09e000061283c",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674184209,
      "updated": 1674184209
    },
    {
      "id": "63ca2e06aff09e00009d9e5f",
      "text": "関連",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674194439,
      "updated": 1674194446
    },
    {
      "id": "63ca0277aff09e000061281f",
      "text": " 線が選択できるか",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674183287,
      "updated": 1674194447
    },
    {
      "id": "63ca028faff09e0000612820",
      "text": " 　線が当たり判定を持っていると要素を動かそうとした時に線にイベントを取られる",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674183312,
      "updated": 1674194452
    },
    {
      "id": "63ca2e36aff09e00009d9e61",
      "text": "\t線の消し方",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674194487,
      "updated": 1674194498
    },
    {
      "id": "63ca2e1faff09e00009d9e60",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674194463,
      "updated": 1674194463
    }
  ]
}